-- ADF Seeks Port Authority Payment for World Trade Center Steel
-- B y   C h r i s   D o l m e t s c h
-- 2013-02-27T18:01:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-27/adf-seeks-port-authority-payment-for-world-trade-center-steel.html
ADF Group Inc. asked a judge to
approve a settlement and order the Port Authority of New York
and  New Jersey  to pay more than $4 million the company says it
is owed for steel it provided for 1 World Trade Center.  To contact the reporter on this story:
